Valentin’s Neo Templar Wololo Tank was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 01 September 2021, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

The Wololo Tank, mainly used for gold, glory, and gospel domination campaign on another habitable planet. This Neo Templar variant is perfect for intergalactic neo crusade warfare. The attached Golden Cross nuclear reactor decorated with Ruby & Emerald Swarovski Crystal not only acts as a weapon of mass destruction but also makes your presence stand out on the battlefield. Full-plated diamond covers the entire surface of this gorgeous beast and creates grand illusions to its enemy.

Advance, Survive, and Flex in Battles.
